\id 1JN - Baga Translation Unicode
\h 1IsaŇč
\toc3 1SAŇä
\toc2 1 IsaŇč
\toc1 Areka Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nŇč…õ IsaŇč …õnacics…õ alaŇč m…Ē
\mt1 1 IsaŇč
\imt1 An'…Ē IsaŇč …Ēy…Ēn…õ-…õ, t'ake t…Ē p…ômar pakaraŇč…õn…õ areka Ňč…Ēn-…õ?
\ip Areka Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča IsaŇč Ňč…Ē ŇčaŇč…õ nŇč…õ anacic meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maas k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (85) k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (95) nt…õ k…ôkom ka Krist k…ônacep…ôr m…Ē. IsaŇč …õnament…ôrn…õ f…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôcic…ôs ka areka ŇčaŇč…õ, mba sapit…ôr s…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē s…ôment…ôr a f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč y…Ē k…ôyi ka Yesu doru k…Ē k…ôf…Ēt…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē k…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr (1.1-3). Tecic…ôs ta areka Ňča IsaŇč t…Ēl…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ k…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē tecic…ôs nt…õ amb…ôp d…ôKawandi ka IsaŇč m…Ē. Anc…õm-c…õmn…õ a IsaŇč …õnacic…ôs Kawandi k…Ēn k…Ē reka ny…õ maas dare da Efesi, nde …õnand…õ m…Ē: Areka Ňča IsaŇč Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, Ňča m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňča maas.
\ip IsaŇč …õnacic…õ alaŇč f…ôp t…õm nt…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč k…ônayi d…ôp…ôcuca pa afum al…Ēma aŇč…õ ancwe ¬ęac…ôr…õ¬Ľ m…Ē. Afum akak…Ē Ňčancc…õm-c…õmn…õ a Yesu Kanu yati …õnay…Ēn…õ, baf…Ē fum …õnayi nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ dis k…Ē mecir p…ôyi ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč m…Ē. It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ IsaŇč k…ôcic…ôs k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ a f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč mes ma k…ôyi doru ka Yesu k…ônacep…ôr haŇč nk…Ēns…ôrka p…ôcgbuŇč…õn…õ Yesu waca w…Ēn yati (1.1-3). IsaŇč …õnacic areka ŇčaŇč…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôlas p…ôbotu p…Ēn m…Ē (1 IsaŇč 1.4), p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ alaŇč k…ôt…Ēciya (1 IsaŇč 2.1), p…ôbum alaŇč m…õt…ôks…õ ma yem (1 IsaŇč 2.26), p…ôyeŇčk…ôs alaŇč b…ôk…ôc k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ a ayac Ňča (5.13).
\iot Tokot…ôr…õn…õ ta moloku ma areka
\io1 1. IsaŇč ement…ôr areka Ňč…Ēn, k'oloku tes nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k'ancic Ňči m…Ē (1.1-4).
\io1 2. IsaŇč …õnas…Ēks…ôr afum nt…õ Kanu k…ôy…Ēn…õ p…ôwaŇčk…ôra m…Ē, p…ômar pacep…ôr…õn…õ doru k…ôyi d…ôp…ôwaŇčk…ôra p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnacep…ôr…õn…õ di m…Ē (1.5-3.10).
\io1 3. Nt…õ t…õnc…ôm…õ ti dar…ôŇč m…Ē, IsaŇč …õnac…õm-c…õm…ôs tosom nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta k…ôb…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē (3.11-5.12).
\io1 4. Moloku m…õlp…ôs (5.13-21).
\c 1
\s1 Toloku ta kiyi w…ôyeŇč
\p 
\v 1 T…Ēk…Ē t…õnayi k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop, nt…õ s…ônane, nt…õ s…ônan…ôŇčk…õ f…Ēr yosu, nt…õ s…ônagb…õk…ôr…õ k…Ē waca wosu woŇčgbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ ti m…Ē, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ toloku ta kiyi w…ôyeŇč.
\v 2 Awa kiyi w…ôyeŇč k…ôment…ôrn…õ, k…Ē s…ôn…ôŇčk ki, s…ônd…ôŇčk sede sa ki, s…ôloku nu kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru, nk…õ k…ônayi Kas k…ôs…ôk ak…Ē k…ôment…ôrn…õ su m…Ē.
\v 3 S…ônd…ôŇčk…ôr n…ôna nt…õ s…ônan…ôŇčk k…Ē s…ône m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôna s…Ē n…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē s…ôna, pat…ôŇčn…õ f…ôp fosu k…Ē Kas k…Ē wan k…Ēn Yesu Krist m…Ē.
\v 4 Tat…Ēk…Ē, s…ôna, s…ôncic ti, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôbotu posu p…õlar…õ m…Ē.
\s1 Kanu p…ôwaŇčk…ôra p…Ē
\p 
\v 5 Tosom nt…õ s…ônanen…õ Krist m…Ē, t…Ē s…ônd…ôŇčk…ôr nu, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu p…ôwaŇčk…ôra p…Ē, kubump nk…õ o nk…õ k…ôyi f…õ k…Ē.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē s…ôloku a s…ônt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn mba s…ôck…Ēt d…ôkubump-…õ, k…ôyem…õ k…Ē s…ônd…õ, s…ôyi f…õ k…ôcy…Ē nt…õ kance k…ôloku m…Ē.
\p 
\v 7 Mba k…Ē s…ôndek…Ēt p…ôwaŇčk…ôra disr…õ, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēns…ôrka eyi p…ôwaŇčk…ôra m…Ē-…õ, s…ôyi k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ disr…õ k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčayi d…ôp…ôwaŇčk…ôra m…Ē, mecir ma Yesu wan k…Ēn mendes…Ēk…ôs su p…ôciya f…ôp.
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē s…ôloku a s…ôy…Ē f…õ kiciya-…õ, k…ôtiŇčk…ôrn…õ k…Ē s…ônd…õ, kance k…ôyi f…õ su.
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē s…ôwos…õ k…ôc…õŇč kiciya kosu-…õ, Kanu k…ôŇčy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ônaloku m…Ē, k…ôlomp, k…ôndeŇčaŇčn…õn…õ su kiciya kosu, k…ôs…Ēk…ôs su p…ôt…Ēlomp f…ôp.
\v 10 K…Ē s…ôloku a s…ônciya f…õ-…õ, s…ôs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôyi p…ôm…Ē Kanu w…ôyem…õ …Ēf…Ē, toloku t…Ēn teyi f…õ su.
\c 2
\s1 Krist ender k…ômar su
\p 
\v 1 Awut em, incic'on tant…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ônciya m…Ē. Mba k…Ē fum enciya-…õ, s…ôy…Ē w…ômar nw…õ eyi nde Papa k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, Yesu Krist, w…ôlompu.
\p 
\v 2 Nk…Ēn yati …Ēy…Ēn…õ poloŇčn…õ mp…õ poŇčkump kiciya kosu m…Ē, baf…Ē kiciya ka s…ôna gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, mba ka aka doru dand…õ f…ôp.
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē s…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom ma Kanu-…õ, s…ôntam k…ôcloku a s…ônc…ôr…õ k…Ē.
\v 4 Nw…õ oŇčloku: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ k…Ē¬Ľ ta w…ôkayi …õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom m…Ēn-…õ, w…ôyem…õ …Ēf…Ē, kance k…ôyi f…õ k…Ē.
\v 5 Mba nw…õ …õŇčm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ toloku t…Ēn m…Ē, kance k…ôyi w…ôkayi, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Kanu k…ômbut f…õ k…Ē. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ a s…ônc…ôr…õ a s…ôyi k…Ē nk…Ēn:
\v 6 Nw…õ oŇčloku k…ôyi k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, p…ômar p…ôk…Ēt p…ôm…Ē Yesu.
\p 
\v 7 N…ôna aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, baf…Ē tosom tofu t'incic'on, mba tosom tokur nt…õ n…ônas…Ēt…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē. Tosom tokur tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ toloku t…Ēk…Ē n…ônane m…Ē.
\v 8 K…ôca k…ôl…Ēma, tosom tofu t'incic'on nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kance nn…Ē Krist eyi m…Ē k…Ē nn…Ē n…ôna n…ôyi m…Ē, bawo kubump k…ôncep…ôr k…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa kance peyi oŇč k…ômar.
\p 
\v 9 Nw…õ oŇčloku k…ôyi d…ôp…ôwaŇčk…ôra mba w…ôkayi p…ôter w…õnc w…ôlaŇč m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi d…ôkubump.
\v 10 Nw…õ …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc w…ôlaŇč m…Ē eyi d…ôp…ôwaŇčk…ôra, nn…Ē eyi m…Ē, nt…õ o nt…õ teyi f…õ nt…õ t…õmp…ôt k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 11 Mba nw…õ enter w…õnc w…ôlaŇč m…Ē, d…ôkubump eyi k…ôk…Ēt, …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ nde eyi k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, bawo kubump k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē f…Ēr k…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk.
\s1 K…ôt…õf…ôrn…õ ka doru k…Ē ka ater a Krist
\q1 
\v 12 K…ôcic'on k'ind…õ awut em,
\q2 bawo aŇčaŇčn…õn'on kiciya konu teta tewe ta Krist.
\q1 
\v 13 K…ôcic'on k'ind…õ, papa aŇča,
\q2 bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ w…ôk…Ē …õnayi k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē.
\q1 K…ôcic'on k'ind…õ, n…ôna at…õmp,
\q2 bawo n…ôntam W…ôl…õc, Sentani.
\q1 
\v 14 Incic'on awut em,
\q2 bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ Papa Kanu.
\q1 Incic'on papa aŇča,
\q2 bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ w…ôk…Ē …õnayi k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē.
\q1 Incic'on n…ôna at…õmp,
\q2 bawo n…ôy…Ē s…Ēk…ôt,
\q2 k…Ē toloku ta Kanu teyi nu,
\q2 k…Ē n…ôntam W…ôl…õc, Sentani.
\p 
\v 15 Ta n…ôb…Ēt…ôr mes ma doru, ta n…ôb…Ēt…ôr s…Ē daka da doru. K…Ē fum …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr mes ma doru-…õ, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Papa Kanu k…ôf…Ēyi k…Ē.
\v 16 Bawo daka o daka nd…õ deyi doru m…Ē, baf…Ē ndena Papa Kanu d…õŇčy…õf…õ, mba da doru dand…õ d…Ē. K…ôy…õf…õ t…õfaŇč t…õl…õc ta dis k…ôk…Ē t…õfaŇč t…õl…õc ta f…Ēr k…ôb…ôp ka k…ôlaŇč ka k…ôdot banca ka k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka daka dad…Ēk…Ē, mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp doru dand…õ d…Ēy…Ē mi.
\v 17 Doru dand…õ dendelip k…Ē m…õfaŇč m…õl…õc ma di, mba m…ôna nw…õ m…ônc…ôm…õ t…õfaŇč ta Kanu dar…ôŇč m…Ē, m…ôŇčyi w…ôyeŇč doru o doru.
\b
\p 
\v 18 Awut em, dec d…õlp…ôs d'ayi dand…õ! N…ônane pacloku a w…ôter ka Krist endeder. Kance k…Ē: Ater a Krist Ňčala oŇč nd…õk…ôl. It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ s…ônc…ôr…õn…õ a dec d…õlp…ôs d…õmb…ôp m…Ē.
\v 19 Ňäanawur k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ kosu disr…õ, mba baf…Ē akosu Ňčanayi. Bawo Ňčanay…Ēn…õ akosu-…õ, k…Ē Ňčanader Ňčayi k…Ē s…ôna. Tement…ôrn…õ ali w…ôkin Ňča dac…Ē …õnay…Ēn…õ f…õ w…ôkosu.
\v 20 K…Ē n…ôna, n…ôs…Ēt…ôr Krist Amera Ňäecempi, it'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ f…ôp fonu n…ônc…ôr…õ kance m…Ē.
\v 21 Incic'on, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…õ a n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ kance, mba bawo ali yem yin yeyi f…õ d…ôkance nk…õ n…ônc…ôr…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 22 An'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôyem…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ nw…õ ence k…ôloku a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist m…Ē-…õ? Awa w…ôkak…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôter ka Krist, w…ôkak…Ē ece Papa Kanu k…Ē Wan.
\v 23 Nw…õ o nw…õ ence Wan m…Ē, …Ēy…Ē f…õ s…Ē Papa Kanu. Nw…õ owos…õ p…ôloku s…Ē teta Wan m…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ē s…Ē Papa Kanu.
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē n…ôna, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ t…Ēk…Ē n…ônane k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē. K…Ē n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ t…Ēk…Ē n…ônane k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē-…õ, n…ôna s…Ē n…ôŇčyi d…ôWan k…Ē d…ôKas.
\v 25 Temer nt…õ Krist …õnas…ĒŇč su m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru.
\p 
\v 26 Incic'on tant…õ teta ak…Ē ŇčantiŇčk…ôr'un m…Ē.
\v 27 K…Ē n…ôna, k…ôb…Ēy ka Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēk…Ē n…ônas…Ēt…ôr Krist m…Ē, k…ôyi nu. K…ôder ka fum k…ôdet…ôks'on k…ôy…Ē f…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē, bawo k…ôb…Ēy k…Ēn k…ônt…ôks'on mes f…ôp. K…ôb…Ēy ka Amera Ňäecempi kaŇčk…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ kance, k…ôy…Ē f…õ yem. Awa! N…ôsump…ôr k…ôyi d…ôKrist p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ôb…Ēy ka Amera Ňäecempi k…ônat…ôks'on m…Ē.
\s1 Awut a Kanu
\p 
\v 28 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč awut em, n…ôsump…ôr k…ôyi d…ôKrist, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ t…õm nt…õ o nt…õ Krist endement…ôrn…õ m…Ē, pat…Ēmp…ôr k…ôb…ôkn…õ ta malap mm…õ o mm…õ m…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôb…Ēl…õ k…Ē t…õm ta k…ôder k…Ēn.
\v 29 K…Ē n…ônc…ôr…õ a Krist olomp-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ s…Ē a nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēt p…ôlompu disr…õ m…Ē, dokom da Kanu d'…õy…õf…õ.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 N…ôm…Ēm…ôn ma k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…ôp…ĒŇč nk…õ Papa Kanu …Ēs…ĒŇč su m…Ē, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ pacwe su ¬ęawut a Kanu.¬Ľ Ňäa Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ yati! K'afum a doru Ňčant…Ēc…ôr…õ su-…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a Ňčanc…ôr…õ f…õ Kanu.
\p 
\v 2 N…ôna aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, nd…õk…ôl oŇč awut a Kanu Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ. Teyi nt…õ s…ôndeyi m…Ē t…õntament…ôrn…õ f…õ k…ôr…õsna. Mba s…ônc…ôr…õ a t…õm o t…õm nt…õ Krist endement…ôrn…õ m…Ē, s…ôndewur…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn, bawo s…ônden…ôŇčk k…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē eyi m…Ē.
\v 3 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôgb…õk…ôr amera kaŇčk…Ē, …ĒŇčs…Ēk…ôsn…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Krist …Ēs…Ēk m…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 Nw…õ o nw…õ enciya m…Ē, baf…Ē sariy…õ sa Kanu s'…õnc…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč. Bawo kiciya, k…ôyeŇčk…ôr ka sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē domp k…Ē.
\v 5 Awa! N…ônc…ôr…õ ti, Krist …õnament…ôrn…õ k…ôdeliŇč kiciya. K…Ē nk…Ēn, kiciya k…ôyi f…õ k…Ē.
\v 6 Nw…õ o nw…õ eyi k…Ē Krist m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēciya. Nw…õ o nw…õ enciya m…Ē …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ k…Ē, ali katin …õn…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē.
\p 
\v 7 Awut em, ta fum o fum p…ôtiŇčk…ôr nu! Nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ē tes tolompu m…Ē, w…ôlompu …Ēf…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Krist olomp m…Ē.
\v 8 Nw…õ enciya m…Ē d…ôŇč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc …õy…õf…õ, bawo Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õnaciya k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop. K…Ē Wan ka Kanu …õnament…ôrn…õ-…õ, teta k…ôl…ôs…ôr ka y…õb…ôc ya Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc k…ônayi.
\v 9 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčy…õf…õ dokom da Kanu m…Ē …Ēf…Ēciya, bawo defet da Kanu, nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ toloku t…Ēn m…Ē, deyi k…Ē. W…ôkayi …Ēf…Ētam k…ôciya bawo d…ôKanu …õy…õf…õ.
\v 10 Ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õn…õp…ôl…õ ta ay…õf…õ dokom da Kanu k…Ē ay…õf…õ dokom da Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc: Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē p…ôlompu m…Ē, baf…Ē dokom da Kanu d'…õy…õf…õ, tin tayi t…Ē k…Ē nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc w…ôlaŇč m…Ē.
\s1 Pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ!
\p 
\v 11 Tosom tant…õ t…Ē n…ônane k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop: Pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ!
\v 12 Ta pay…Ē p…ôm…Ē Kay…õn, nw…õ …õnay…õf…õ d…ôW…ôl…õc, Sentani, k'endif w…õnc m…Ē. T'ake t'…õnadif…õ k…Ē-…õ? Bawo y…õb…ôc y…Ēn y…õnalomp f…õ, ya w…õnc yolomp.
\p 
\v 13 Aw…õnc im aŇča, ta teciyan…õn'on k'afum a doru Ňčanter nu-…õ.
\v 14 S…ôna, s…ônc…ôr…õ a nde defi deyi m…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē nde kiyi w…ôyeŇč k…ôyi m…Ē, bawo s…ômb…Ēt…ôr aw…õnc asu alaŇč. Nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc m…Ē, eyi nde defi deyi m…Ē.
\v 15 Nw…õ o nw…õ enter w…õnc m…Ē w…ôdif fum …Ēf…Ē. N…ônc…ôr…õ ali w…ôdif fum w…ôkin, kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru k…ôyi f…õ k…Ē.
\v 16 Tant…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr: Krist …Ēs…ĒŇč kiyi w…ôyeŇč k…Ēn teta s…ôna. S…ôna s…Ē p…ômar s…ôs…ĒŇč kiyi w…ôyeŇč kosu teta aw…õnc asu alaŇč.
\v 17 Mba k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …Ēy…Ē daka da doru, p…ôn…ôŇčk w…õnc w…ôlaŇč p…ôyi d…ôp…ôcuca, mba p…ôgb…ôt…ôr w…õnc w…ôkak…Ē ab…ôk…ôc-…õ, c…ôke c…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Kanu k…ôyi w…ôkayi-…õ?
\v 18 Awut em, ta pay…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka d…ômoloku k…Ē d…ôtemer gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, mba pay…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr nk…õ k…ôŇčment…ôrn…õ d…ôm…Ēy…Ē k…Ē d…ôkance m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôlaŇč ka afum Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč
\p 
\v 19 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôc…ôr…õ a aka kance Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ, b…ôk…ôc yosu y…Ēf…Ēr Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 20 Bawo k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yosu yoloku a s…ônciya-…õ, Kanu k…ômb…õk k…ôtas yi, k…Ē k…ônc…ôr…õ mes f…ôp.
\v 21 N…ôna aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yosu y…Ēnt…Ēloku su a s…ônciya-…õ, s…ôy…Ē k…ôb…ôkn…õ nde Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē.
\v 22 Nt…õ o nt…õ s…ôntola m…Ē s…ôŇčs…Ēt…ôr k…Ē ti, bawo s…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom m…Ēn, k…Ē s…ôŇčy…Ē s…Ē mes mm…õ m…Ēmb…Ēt k…Ē m…Ē.
\p 
\v 23 Tosom t…Ēn t…õnt…õ: Pagb…õk…ôr tewe ta wan k…Ēn Yesu Krist k…ôlaŇč, pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē tosom t…Ēk…Ē …õnasom su m…Ē.
\v 24 M…ôna nw…õ m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, m…ôyi d…ôKanu, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ Kanu k…ôyi d…ôm…ôna w…ôkayi m…Ē. Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč su m…Ē, Ňč…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ a Kanu k…ôyi su.
\c 4
\s1 Amera Ňča Kanu k…Ē Ňča w…ôter…õn…õ k…Ēn
\p 
\v 1 N…ôna aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, ta n…ôlaŇč ak…Ē ŇčabaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…Ē Amera m…Ē f…ôp. Mba n…ôk…Ēkc…õ yi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôtam k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ ya d…ôKanu y…Ē-…õ, bawo sayib…õ sa yem s…ôlar…ôm s…ôsams…ôr doru.
\v 2 Tant…õ disr…õ n…ôntam k…ôc…ôr…õ a Amera Ňča Kanu Ňč…Ē: Amera nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ ŇčoŇčwos…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ a Yesu Krist …õnader p…ôy…Ēn…õ fum m…Ē, Ňča Kanu Ňč…Ē.
\v 3 Mba amera nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēnt…Ēwos…õ k…ôloku a Yesu …õnader c…ôfum m…Ē, baf…Ē Ňča Kanu Ňč…Ē, Ňča w…ôter Krist Ňč…Ē. N…ônane pacloku a k…ôder k…Ē w…ôter ka Krist …õnd…õ, nd…õk…ôl oŇč eyi doru.
\p 
\v 4 N…ôna awut em, aka Kanu Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ, k…Ē n…ôntam sayib…õ sa yem, bawo nw…õ eyi nu m…Ē, …õntas nw…õ eyi doru m…Ē.
\v 5 Ňäa, aka doru Ňč…Ē. Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ moloku maŇčan m…Ēy…Ēn…õ ma doru m…Ē, k…Ē doru d…õnc…ôŇčk…ôl Ňča.
\v 6 S…ôna, aka Kanu Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ. Nw…õ …õnc…ôr…õ Kanu m…Ē, …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl su. Nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka Kanu m…Ē …Ēf…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl su. Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôc…ôr…õ amera Ňča kance k…Ē amera Ňča k…ôtiŇčk…ôr.
\s1 Kanu, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē
\p 
\v 7 N…ôna aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ,
\q1 bawo k…ôb…Ēt…ôr dokom da Kanu d…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ.
\q1 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēb…Ēt…ôr, dokom da Kanu d'…õy…õf…õ,
\q1 k'…õnc…ôr…õ s…Ē Kanu.
\q1 
\v 8 Nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ Kanu ali katin,
\q1 bawo Kanu, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē.
\q1 
\v 9 Tant…õ t…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Kanu k…ônament…ôrn…õ su dac…Ē:
\q1 K…Ē Kanu k…ôsom wan k…Ēn sona doru nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ômar su s…ôs…Ēt…ôr k…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 10 K…ôb…Ēt…ôr kaŇčk…Ē,
\q1 baf…Ē s…ôn'…Ēb…Ēt…ôr Kanu,
\q1 mba nk…Ēn …Ēb…Ēt…ôr su.
\q1 K…Ē Kanu k…ômb…Ēt…ôr su haŇč k…Ē k…ôsom wan k…Ēn,
\q1 nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ poloŇčn…õ mp…õ poŇčkump kiciya kosu m…Ē.
\m 
\v 11 N…ôna aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ômb…Ēt…ôr su tant…õ-…õ, p…ômar s…ôna alaŇč s…Ē f…ôp pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ.
\v 12 Ali katin fum o fum …õŇčgb…ôtn…õ f…õ Kanu. K…Ē s…ômb…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ-…õ, Kanu k…ôŇčyi su dac…Ē, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ēn k…ôf…Ēbut su.
\v 13 Tant…õ t…Ē s…ôntam k…ôc…ôr…õ a s…ôyi d…ôKanu, k…Ē Kanu k…ôyi d…ôs…ôna: Bawo …Ēs…ĒŇč su Amera Ňč…Ēn.
\v 14 K…Ē s…ôna s…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ, k…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ sede a Papa osom Wan k…ôdey…Ēn…õ w…ôyac ka doru.
\p 
\v 15 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčwos…õ k…ôloku a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Wan ka Kanu m…Ē, Kanu k…ôŇčyi k…Ē, nk…Ēn s…Ē p…ôyi d…ôKanu.
\v 16 K…Ē s…ôna, s…ônc…ôr…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr nk…õ Kanu k…ômb…Ēt…ôr su m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôŇčgb…õk…ôr k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôlaŇč.
\p Kanu, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē. Nw…õ eŇčyi k…ôb…Ēt…ôr disr…õ m…Ē, eyi d…ôKanu, Kanu k…ôyi d…ôw…ôkayi.
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kosu k…ônt…Ēbut-…õ, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôb…ôkn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Kanu k…ôŇčkiti su m…Ē. Ta ake-…õ? Bawo kiyi kosu doru k…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē ka Yesu Krist.
\v 18 K…ônes…õ k…ôyi f…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr disr…õ. K…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…ônt…Ēbut-…õ, k…ômb…õl…ôs k…ônes…õ. Bawo k…ônes…õ k…ônc…õm-c…õm…ôs a k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…ôndeder. W…ônes…õ, k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…ômbut k…Ē.
\v 19 K…Ē s…ôna, s…ômb…Ēt…ôr, bawo Kanu k…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr su.
\v 20 K…Ē fum oloku: ¬ęImb…Ēt…ôr Kanu¬Ľ mba p…ôter w…õnc w…ôlaŇč-…õ, w…ôyem…õ …Ēf…Ē, bawo nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc nw…õ …õŇčn…ôŇčk m…Ē, …Ēf…Ētam k…ôb…Ēt…ôr Kanu nk…õ …Ēnt…Ēn…ôŇčk m…Ē.
\v 21 Tosom tant…õ t…Ē Kanu k…ônasom su: Nw…õ …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr Kanu m…Ē, p…ômar p…ôb…Ēt…ôr s…Ē w…õnc.
\c 5
\s1 K…ôtam kosu ka doru
\p 
\v 1 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õlaŇč a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist m…Ē, fum w…ôkak…Ē dokom da Kanu d'…õy…õf…õ. Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr w…ôkomb…ôra m…Ē, …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr s…Ē nw…õ …õy…õf…õ dokom da w…ôkayi m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē s…ômb…Ēt…ôr Kanu, s…ôc…ôm…õ s…Ē mosom m…Ēn dar…ôŇč-…õ, s…ôntam k…ôc…ôr…õ a s…ômb…Ēt…ôr awut a Kanu.
\v 3 Bawo k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Kanu k…ôy…Ēn…õ a s…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom m…Ēn. Mosom mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēf…Ēt…Ēr…ôs,
\v 4 bawo nw…õ o nw…õ …õy…õf…õ dokom da Kanu m…Ē, …õntam doru. Tes nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôtam doru m…Ē, it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôlaŇč kosu.
\p 
\v 5 An'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtam ka doru-…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ nw…õ …õlaŇč a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Wan ka Kanu m…Ē?
\v 6 Nk…Ēn Yesu Krist nw…õ …õnader su k…Ē domun da k…ôgb…ôt k…Ēn d…ôromun k…Ē mecir ma defi d…Ēn m…Ē, baf…Ē domun gb…ôc…ôr…ôm d'…õnak…õr…õ, mba domun k…Ē mecir. Amera Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč sede sas…Ēk…Ē, bawo Amera Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ kance.
\v 7 Awa ca maas y…Ēs…ĒŇč sede sa ti:
\v 8 Amera, domun k…Ē mecir, ca yay…õ maas f…ôp y…õnt…ôŇčn…õ ti.
\v 9 K…Ē s…ôwos…õ sede sa afum-…õ, sede sa Kanu s…ômb…õk s…ôtas si. Bawo sede sa Kanu s…ônt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč sede teta Wan k…Ēn.
\v 10 Nw…õ …õŇčgb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn nde Wan ka Kanu eyi m…Ē, …Ēy…Ē sede sas…Ēk…Ē d'nk…Ēns…ôrka. Nw…õ …Ēnt…ĒlaŇč Kanu m…Ē, …õŇčgb…õk…ôl kance nk…õ Kanu k…ônaloku m…Ē, bawo …õŇčgb…õk…ôr f…õ k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn d…ôsede ns…õ Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč teta Wan k…Ēn m…Ē.
\p 
\v 11 Sede sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôment…ôr a Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč su kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru. Kiyi w…ôyeŇč kaŇčk…Ē, d…ôWan k…Ēn k…ôyi.
\v 12 Nw…õ …Ēy…Ē Wan m…Ē, …Ēy…Ē s…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč. Nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē Wan ka Kanu m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēy…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč.
\s1 Kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru
\p 
\v 13 Tat…Ēk…Ē, incic'on ti, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôc…ôr…õ a n…ôy…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru m…Ē, n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôŇčgb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč konu nde tewe ta Wan ka Kanu teyi m…Ē.
\v 14 K…ôbaŇčs…õ nk…õ s…ôy…Ē nn…Ē tewe ta Wan ka Kanu teyi m…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ, k…Ē s…ôntola k…Ē paka mp…õ o mp…õ t…õfaŇč t…Ēn disr…õ-…õ, …õmbaŇč su.
\v 15 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a s…ônc…ôr…õ a …õmbaŇč su-…õ, mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē s…ôntola k…Ē, s…ôŇčs…Ēt…ôr k…Ē pi.
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē fum …õn…ôŇčk w…õnc w…ôlaŇč p…ôcciya kiciya nk…õ k…ônt…Ēsol…õ k…Ē d…ôdefi m…Ē, p…ôtolan…õ k…Ē Kanu, w…õnc w…ôkak…Ē …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč. Afum ak…Ē Ňčanciya kiciya nk…õ k…ônt…Ēsol…õ d…ôdefi m…Ē, Ňč'iŇčloku taŇčan. Kiciya k…ôyi nk…õ k…ôsol…õ d…ôdefi m…Ē, baf…Ē kiciya kaŇčk…Ē k'iŇčloku a patolan…õ ki de.
\v 17 K…ôt…Ēlomp nk…õ o nk…õ, kiciya k…Ē. Mba kiciya k…ôyi nk…õ k…ôt…Ēsol…õ d…ôdefi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 18 S…ônc…ôr…õ a nw…õ o nw…õ …õy…õf…õ dokom da Kanu m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēciya. Bawo nw…õ …õy…õf…õ dokom da Kanu m…Ē ombum w…ôkayi, W…ôl…õc, Sentani, …Ēf…ĒgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē.
\v 19 S…ônc…ôr…õ a aka Kanu Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ, mba aka doru f…ôp Ňčayi k…ôtam ka W…ôl…õc, Sentani d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 20 Mba s…ônc…ôr…õ s…Ē a Wan ka Kanu …õnader k…ôdes…ĒŇč su k…ôs…Ēk domp, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôc…ôr…õ nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ Kance m…Ē. D…ôKance ayi, d…ôk…ômar ka Wan k…Ēn Yesu Krist. Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka kance yati k…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru.
\p 
\v 21 Awut em, n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ m…õr…ôŇčka.
